  "texts": [
    "For instance, smart wearable technologies (e.g., glasses, headsets) supported by high-speed networks like (e.g., 5G/6G) would allow students to access the metaverse world instantaneously, with no restrictions in terms of time or place.",
    "Importantly, it is vital to incorporate gamification elements into metaverse-based learning platforms.",
    "Gamification can be a powerful tool for increasing perceived enjoyment of use in metaverse-based learning.",
    "By incorporating game-like elements such as badges, leaderboards, and rewards, learners are more likely to feel a sense of accomplishment and enjoyment as they progress through the learning experience.",
    "Furthermore, SE is realised as a key enabler for both PU and PEU."
